item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Bandwidth_Projection Datatype Description SoftLayer_Container_Bandwidth_Projection models projected bandwidth use over a time range. associatedMethods SoftLayer_Bandwidth_Manager::getBandwidthList Local allowedUsage Bandwidth limit for this hardware. Type: string estimatedUsage Estimated bandwidth usage so far this billing cycle. Type: string hardwareId Hardware ID of server to monitor. Type: integer projectedUsage Projected usage for this hardware based on previous usage this billing cycle.
